{"tid":2305959,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙豐正考慮完全退出美國的零售銀行業務","createTime":"2020-11-30T05:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T05:55:08.000Z","uid":174960,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6acccbe635c54cf2db616caca40542d755f54eb9","tid":2305959,"uid":174960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:49:08.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國傳媒報道，滙豐正考慮完全退出美國的零售銀行業務。<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》引述消人士指，滙豐正尋求重新分配資源，以改善銀行業務表現，正考慮將資源從美國轉移到盈利表現更佳的亞洲，滙豐高層將在未來數星期，向董事會提交有關計劃。<br />\n<br />\n不過消息指，滙豐仍未就相關計劃作最後決定，正研究撤資成本的財務可行性。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐在美國從事零售銀行業務四十年，不過近年在北美洲的業務盈利不斷萎縮。在美國今年首三季的稅前盈利，虧損近五億二千萬美元，而在過去兩年，合共全年虧損超過四億六千萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=414694\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414694&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGicZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=86a7c96c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414694&h=494d239b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=414694</a>"},{"pid":"528528e3d83899d25bed466ef02801c9627b2615","tid":2305959,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f287ab28ec1c47da141430167a30f1961a470c0","tid":2305959,"uid":187770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"完全變中資?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d893602e3778a63eae5b6a7b05998ebd61c77ca","tid":2305959,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T05:55:08.000Z","msg":"retail生意佔銀行收益幾多成?"}]}